  <entry>
    <title>go time包为什么饱受争议？</title>
    <link href="https://www.yeebing.cn/2022/12/17/go/time/"/>
    <id>https://www.yeebing.cn/2022/12/17/go/time/</id>
    <published>2022-12-17T14:04:12.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-03-07T08:25:52.412Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="背景"><a href="#背景" class="headerlink" title="背景"></a>背景</h2><p>Go time 包是一大痛点，主要原因就是Time类型的format方式。所以我会以Format作为Go time包的切入点。</p><h3 id="坑点展示"><a href="#坑点展示" class="headerlink" title="坑点展示"></a>坑点展示</h3><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">n := time.Now()</span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(n)</span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(n.Format(<span class="string">&quot;2006-01-02 15:04:05&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(n.Format(<span class="string">&quot;2007-01-02 15:04:05&quot;</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行结果：</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/12/17/t6k7OCgdfTYKrmG.png" alt="image-20221217222159791"></p><p>仔细看我第四行代码将2006改成了2007，format出来的year就是一个莫名其妙的数字。</p><p>原因是Go要求format必须是2006-01-02 15:04:05 这些数字，即年份不能用其他年份表示，月份、日期也是如此。</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="其他语言的format方式"><a href="#其他语言的format方式" class="headerlink" title="其他语言的format方式"></a>其他语言的format方式</h2><p>这是一段Java的时间格式化代码。</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">StringBuilder</span> <span class="variable">sb</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">StringBuilder</span>();</span><br><span class="line">sb.append(<span class="string">&quot;yyyy年MM月dd日 HH:mm:ss&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    .append(<span class="string">&quot; 上下午标志 a&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    .append(<span class="string">&quot; E&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    .append(<span class="string">&quot; 一年中的第D天&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    .append(<span class="string">&quot; 一月中的第F个星期&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    .append(<span class="string">&quot; 一年中的第w个星期&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    .append(<span class="string">&quot; 一月中的第W个星期&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    .append(<span class="string">&quot; Z&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    .append(<span class="string">&quot; z&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">SimpleDateFormat</span> <span class="variable">sdf</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">SimpleDateFormat</span>(sb.toString());</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">dateString</span> <span class="operator">=</span> sdf.format(<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Date</span>());</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(dateString);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/12/17/XGdUSMhJky864VY.png" alt="img"></p><p>Java 采用的yymmdd的方式来实现日期格式化。通俗来讲就是使用特定的字符来代替时间，如y代表year。</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/12/17/On9ceINwVv2TXhQ.png" alt="img"></p><p>它将各个常用及不常用但必须的日期格式（如年、月、日，星期、周数、时区等）都用字符表示出来，使用者只管考虑怎么连接这些字符，得到想要的日期字符串。难怪Go的日期格式化饱受诟病。</p><p>Go 官方的解释是这样的：<code>Jan 2 3:04 pm 06 -0700 </code>这样就是完美的1 2 3 4 5 6 7</p><h2 id="如何解决（从自身出发）"><a href="#如何解决（从自身出发）" class="headerlink" title="如何解决（从自身出发）"></a>如何解决（从自身出发）</h2><p><strong>1.这串奇怪的时间的记忆方法</strong></p><p>官方给出的记忆方法（但对我来说也不好记）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1: month (January, Jan, 01, etc)</span><br><span class="line">2: day</span><br><span class="line">3: hour (15 is 3pm on a 24 hour clock)</span><br><span class="line">4: minute</span><br><span class="line">5: second</span><br><span class="line">6: year (2006)</span><br><span class="line">7: timezone (GMT-7 is MST)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>2.利用好IDE的语法提示</strong></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/12/17/iEojDtULslBJqG4.png" alt="image-20221217222517160"></p><p>第二处因为没有采用2006的年份，Goland很贴心的给出了灰色的标记。</p><p>而第三处虽然删去了年份的前两位，月份、日期的前导“0”，但是依旧是可以正常使用的，Goland也贴心的没有给提示。</p><p><strong>3. 使用标准库提供的常量</strong></p><p>既然自己容易写错，那么可以使用官方提供的一系列常量来解决。但是如何记住这些常量和他们的用法又是一种心理负担了，而且我自认为这些常量的名称往往过于“抽象”，可能还没直接写数字来得方便。</p><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> (</span><br><span class="line">ANSIC       = <span class="string">&quot;Mon Jan _2 15:04:05 2006&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">UnixDate    = <span class="string">&quot;Mon Jan _2 15:04:05 MST 2006&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">RubyDate    = <span class="string">&quot;Mon Jan 02 15:04:05 -0700 2006&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">RFC822      = <span class="string">&quot;02 Jan 06 15:04 MST&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">RFC822Z     = <span class="string">&quot;02 Jan 06 15:04 -0700&quot;</span> <span class="comment">// RFC822 with numeric zone</span></span><br><span class="line">RFC850      = <span class="string">&quot;Monday, 02-Jan-06 15:04:05 MST&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">RFC1123     = <span class="string">&quot;Mon, 02 Jan 2006 15:04:05 MST&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">RFC1123Z    = <span class="string">&quot;Mon, 02 Jan 2006 15:04:05 -0700&quot;</span> <span class="comment">// RFC1123 with numeric zone</span></span><br><span class="line">RFC3339     = <span class="string">&quot;2006-01-02T15:04:05Z07:00&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">RFC3339Nano = <span class="string">&quot;2006-01-02T15:04:05.999999999Z07:00&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">Kitchen     = <span class="string">&quot;3:04PM&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Handy time stamps.</span></span><br><span class="line">Stamp      = <span class="string">&quot;Jan _2 15:04:05&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">StampMilli = <span class="string">&quot;Jan _2 15:04:05.000&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">StampMicro = <span class="string">&quot;Jan _2 15:04:05.000000&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">StampNano  = <span class="string">&quot;Jan _2 15:04:05.000000000&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> (</span><br><span class="line">_                        = <span class="literal">iota</span></span><br><span class="line">stdLongMonth             = <span class="literal">iota</span> + stdNeedDate  <span class="comment">// &quot;January&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">stdMonth                                       <span class="comment">// &quot;Jan&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">stdNumMonth                                    <span class="comment">// &quot;1&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">stdZeroMonth                                   <span class="comment">// &quot;01&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">stdLongWeekDay                                 <span class="comment">// &quot;Monday&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="标准库实现"><a href="#标准库实现" class="headerlink" title="标准库实现"></a>标准库实现</h2><p>在好奇心的驱使下，我想看看标准库的time包是怎么实现Format这个函数的，为什么会产生这个效果。</p><p>大致原理就是使用一个for循环去拆解用户提供的format字符串，每次拆解出一个单位（标准库认为的可以替换的一些字符），如何使用switch case 来判断该字符属于上面提到的哪种常量，根据常量定义的规则（如stdZeroMonth表示月份有前导“0”）将格式化后的日期append到要返回的字符串上。</p><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 缩略后的源码</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 入参layout就是用户要格式化的日期。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// b 这里可以简单理解成要输出的日期字符串。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="params">(t Time)</span></span> AppendFormat(b []<span class="type">byte</span>, layout <span class="type">string</span>) []<span class="type">byte</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// ... 做一些处理，大概是获取原始时间t的一些状态，方便后面状态机处理</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Each iteration generates one std value.</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> layout != <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> &#123; <span class="comment">// for 循环拆解layout</span></span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 获取词法单元std， 词法单元的前缀prefix，以及后面未处理的内容（重新赋值给layout，用于下次处理）</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 那么nextStdChunk里面就是一个更纯粹的词法分析器，比较一个个‘字符’，来获取词法单元。</span></span><br><span class="line">prefix, std, suffix := nextStdChunk(layout)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> prefix != <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">b = <span class="built_in">append</span>(b, prefix...)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> std == <span class="number">0</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">break</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">layout = suffix</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Compute year, month, day if needed.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> year &lt; <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; std&amp;stdNeedDate != <span class="number">0</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">year, month, day, yday = absDate(abs, <span class="literal">true</span>)</span><br><span class="line">yday++</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Compute hour, minute, second if needed.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> hour &lt; <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; std&amp;stdNeedClock != <span class="number">0</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">hour, min, sec = absClock(abs)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 判断该std属于哪个部分</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">switch</span> std &amp; stdMask &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> stdYear:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// ....</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> stdLongYear:</span><br><span class="line">b = appendInt(b, year, <span class="number">4</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> stdMonth:</span><br><span class="line">b = <span class="built_in">append</span>(b, month.String()[:<span class="number">3</span>]...)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> stdLongMonth:</span><br><span class="line">m := month.String()</span><br><span class="line">b = <span class="built_in">append</span>(b, m...)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> stdNumMonth:</span><br><span class="line">b = appendInt(b, <span class="type">int</span>(month), <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> stdZeroMonth:</span><br><span class="line">b = appendInt(b, <span class="type">int</span>(month), <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> stdWeekDay:</span><br><span class="line">b = <span class="built_in">append</span>(b, absWeekday(abs).String()[:<span class="number">3</span>]...)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> stdLongWeekDay:</span><br><span class="line">s := absWeekday(abs).String()</span><br><span class="line">b = <span class="built_in">append</span>(b, s...)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> stdDay:</span><br><span class="line">b = appendInt(b, day, <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// ..... 很多很多</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> b</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个就和编程语言的词法分析很像了，按照词法单元去拆分代码，同时使用switch来判断匹配到了哪个词法，根据不同的词法进行不同的处理。</p><p>其他语言的yymmdd的日期格式化方式应该跟Go的实现角度差不多，只不过Go采用了2006-01-02 来代替yyyy-mm-dd（猜想，没有看Java代码证实）</p><h2 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h2><p>Go源码</p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_27093465/article/details/53034427">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_27093465/article/details/53034427</a></p><p><a href="https://pkg.go.dev/time#Parse">https://pkg.go.dev/time#Parse</a></p><p><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/366830553">https://www.zhihu.com/question/366830553</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
